"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-19-Chinese-mainland-Olympians-to-visit-Hong-Kong-SAR-govt-1wbzmaoqG4M-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  A delegation of Chinese mainland athletes returning from the Paris 2024 Olympic Games will visit Hong Kong from August 29 to 31, the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (HKSAR) government announced on Sunday.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9999691060724826, \"rank\": 3.089488193711214e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9891543971653821, \"rank\": 0.01093020449451811, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9542935084858089, \"rank\": 0.047881114608236124, \"text\": \"Hong Kong Special Administrative Region\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The delegation will attend a welcome reception and welcome banquet hosted by the HKSAR government, and visit the Hong Kong Sports Institute for exchange activities.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Sports_Institute\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hong Kong Sports Institute\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Sports_Institute\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Sports_Institute\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Members will also attend three public events, including a Gala Show at Queen Elizabeth Stadium on August 30, and give sports demonstrations at Queen Elizabeth Stadium and Victoria Park Swimming Pool on August 31.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"John Lee, chief executive of the HKSAR, expressed his sincere gratitude to the central government for arranging another visit of the Chinese mainland Olympians delegation, which he said \\\"fully demonstrates its care for Hong Kong.\\\"\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lee_(government_official)\", \"score\": 0.8026218482808528, \"rank\": 0.059701492537309275, \"text\": \"John Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lee_(government_official)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lee_(government_official)\"}, {\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9999691060724826, \"rank\": 3.089488193711214e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese mainland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9891543971653821, \"rank\": 0.01093020449451811, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Athletes of the national team, with their spirit of perseverance and high level of skills, achieved breakthroughs in a number of sports in this year's Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The national team achieved its best performance abroad since it comprehensively participated in the 1984 Summer Olympics,\\\" said Lee.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9971485372094462, \"rank\": 0.0016752339801719912, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are extremely proud to have witnessed China's competitive sports continue to scale new heights.\\\"\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9262020088308144, \"rank\": 0.07966074288885812, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The visit of national team athletes to Hong Kong is a decades-long tradition.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9891543971653821, \"rank\": 0.01093020449451811, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The visits of athletes of the national team to Hong Kong in the past have always been a craze in the city, bringing a joyful and festive atmosphere to the community,\\\" said the chief executive.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9891543971653821, \"rank\": 0.01093020449451811, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are looking forward to the delegation's visit to share with Hong Kong people their journey of perseverance and success, and to promote the spirit of Chinese sports.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1789, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9891543971653821, \"rank\": 0.01093020449451811, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5934026174707759, \"rank\": 0.6709842842108198, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hong Kong people will be able to share the national team's joy and triumphs, thereby strengthening their patriotic passion and national spirit, especially among the younger generation,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9891543971653821, \"rank\": 0.01093020449451811, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Cover: Screen in Victoria Harbor shows Hong Kong Olympians coming back from Paris 2024 Olympics in Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, China, August 12, 2024.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"score\": 0.9999973534487259, \"rank\": 2.4120358392219676e-06, \"text\": \"Victoria\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_Victoria\"}, {\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9891543971653821, \"rank\": 0.01093020449451811, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 2173, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2190, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9542935084858089, \"rank\": 0.047881114608236124, \"text\": \"Hong Kong Special Administrative Region\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 2231, \"end\": 2236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9262020088308144, \"rank\": 0.07966074288885812, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP)  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": []}]}"